Installed using Helm 3.x

https://github.com/containous/traefik-helm-chart/tree/master/traefik

helm repo add traefik https://containous.github.io/traefik-helm-chart
helm install traefik traefik/traefik

For the Helm chart values file:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/containous/traefik-helm-chart/master/traefik/values.yaml

Then update the running Helm release in the cluster:
helm upgrade -f values.yaml traefik traefik/traefik
